BuildRequires:    R-CRAN-future 
BuildRequires:    R-CRAN-coda 
BuildRequires:    R-methods 
Requires:         R-CRAN-progress >= 1.2.0
Requires:         R-CRAN-tensorflow >= 1.13.0
Requires:         R-CRAN-R6 
